 Cell[BoxData[
 "BreakInMonomials"],ExpressionUUID->"94faec60-0b61-43a8-b9a6-be5fee01e8ca"],
 " can decompose an expression into monomials, which is useful to analyse the \
structure of contractions."
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.875028617534668*^9, 
  3.8750287657456408`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"3de5eaab-0336-4d06-9411-\
6fa1989916d0"],

