Cell["2) compare the coefficients with the equation of motion,", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.875411555138961*^9, 3.875411569058079*^9}, {
  3.8754116612207623`*^9, 3.875411670209133*^9}, {3.875909574908988*^9, 
